  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Patterns.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/623607817/RenderMan_Patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091409703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/623607817/RenderMan_Patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091409703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"984\" data-width=\"1750\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"623640641\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Patterns.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"623607817\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"8ece2ab0-9a83-45f8-bacf-745516096a22\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/623607817/RenderMan_Patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091409703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/623607817/RenderMan_Patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091409703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>While Materials control the appearance of an object, patterns control the detail by varying the parameters of the material's Bxdf across a surface. </p><p>This is similar to how texture artists use textures to control the appearance of a material. </p><p>RenderMan ships with a set of patterns that allow texturing, color correction, bumping, and various utility shading systems.</p><p>The patterns can be divided into the following categories:</p><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"91f1ce9d-8ccb-41ea-9b48-1a7834c463e0\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Procedural Textures</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><p>Procedurally create noise and patterns.</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222962\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrChecker</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223097\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrCurvature</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223600\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrFractal</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225517\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrVoronoise</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225558\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrWorley</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224343\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrPhasorNoise</u></a></p></li></ul><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"72c0d358-e010-4086-8129-6c704daff5f1\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Color Nodes</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><p>Create or modify colors in the shading network.</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222617\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrBlackBody</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222644\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrBlend</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223021\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrClamp</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223036\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrColorCorrect</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223066\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrColorSpace</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223444\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrExposure</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223657\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrGamma</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223700\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrHairColor</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224012\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrHSL</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224027\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrInvert</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224038\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrLayeredBlend</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224229\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrMix</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224392\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrProjectionStack</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224458\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrRamp</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224612\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrRemap</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225088\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrThinFilm</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225099\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrThreshold</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225490\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrVary</u></a></p></li></ul><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"7dbaa0bf-78fe-4e47-bc9f-c7c27f1f0dcd\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Geometry Nodes</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><p>You can use these nodes to calculate geometric properties and vectors.</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223198\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrDirt</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223338\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrDispScalarLayer</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223359\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrDispTransform</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223392\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrDispVectorLayer</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223417\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrDot</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223082\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrCross</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223459\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrFacingRatio</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224996\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrTangentField</u></a></p></li></ul><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"583432b6-ee63-4848-b850-3a71790ef6cd\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Scripting Nodes</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222454\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>OSL Patterns</u></a></p></li></ul><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0b016c30-9d5f-415a-b7c8-3cbbb41f6d81\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Utility Nodes </span></strong></p>\n</div></div><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222552\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrAttribute</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224176\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrMatteID</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224365\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrPrimvar</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225473\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrVariable</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225447\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrToFloat</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225462\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrToFloat3</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225035\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrTee</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224902\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrShadedSide</u></a></p></li></ul><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"8ccaabaf-2337-4310-be55-906eaf774da2\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Texture Baking Nodes</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><p>These passthrough patterns are designed to allows users to bake arbitrary pattern networks.</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222597\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrBakeTexture</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222579\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrBakePointCloud</u></a></p></li></ul><p /><h3 id=\"Patterns&amp;Noises-GuidanceforWritingYourOwnPatterns\">Guidance for Writing Your Own Patterns</h3><p>You do not need to be limited to the patterns that RenderMan provides.  If you follow the guidance in <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222454\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>OSL Patterns</u></a> you can build your own patterns.  XPU only runs OSL patterns, while RIS runs both C++ and OSL patterns. </p>"
    }
  },
